# Project-specific English allowed words.
# These are real terms (place names, council acronyms, technical IDs) that
# the standard en_US hunspell dictionary doesn't know about.
# Add to this file rather than .codespellignore for new false positives.

# Acronyms / technical
HPID
PID
SSL
URL
UPRN
APIs

# Property identifier conventions
postcode
postcodes
mapkey
configurable
preconfigured

# Common waste / collection vocabulary
recyclables
biowaste
greenwaste
greenswaste
kerbside

# Software / package names referenced in source descriptions
HACS
Hassio
ICS
JSON
YAML
GraphQL
